  "instructions": [
    "Heat a large pan over medium heat and add a little water to prevent sticking.",
    "Add the chopped onion and cook until it is translucent.",
    "Add the minced garlic and grated ginger and cook for another minute.",
    "Add the diced zucchini and cook until it starts to soften.",
    "Add the kashmiri red chili powder, garam masala, and coriander powder, and stir well.",
    "Pour in the low-fat coconut milk and bring the mixture to a simmer.",
    "Reduce the heat to low and let the curry simmer for 10 minutes, stirring occasionally.",
    "Season the curry with salt to taste.",
    "Garnish with chopped fresh cilantro and serve hot."
